Academy_Award_for_Best_Picture_(1930s)	The Academy Award for Best Picture is one of the Academy Awards of Merit presented annually by the Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences ( AMPAS ) to artists working in the motion picture industry .	The Academy Award for Best Picture is one of the Academy Awards .	2







